'''Jay-Jay Bin''' was the partial name of a [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] that enrolled in [[Fett Club]] to become a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]]. However, they were killed by the Mandalorian instructor, as they were ineligible to apply due to the seventh rule of Fett Club: "No Gungans. Ever."

